graph LR
    Feast[Feast Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Feast -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional Storage)
    Feast -.->|persistent storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL]
    Feast -.->|online store| Redis[Redis 7+]
    Feast -.->|object storage| S3[S3/GCS/Azure Blob]
    Feast -.->|data warehouse| Snowflake[Snowflake]
    Feast -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Feast -->|UI integration| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    Feast -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Feast -.->|auth optional| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    Feast -.->|CA bundle| TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundle]

    %% Integration Points (Components that use Feast)
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|feature engineering| Feast
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -->|training/inference| Feast
    KServe[KServe InferenceServices] -->|real-time features| Feast
    ModelRegistry[Model Registry] -.->|metadata link| Feast

    %% External Services
    Feast -->|model storage| S3Storage[S3-compatible Storage]
    Feast -->|metadata mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    Feast -.->|feature repo sync| GitRepo[Git Repository]

